|                                                              |                                                            | REST YAML composition
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./springboot/SpringRestExceptionHttpServer/index.html}Exception Handling}} | Handle exceptions thrown from REST service methods and map them to HTTP responses. | @ExceptionHandler\
|                                                              |                                                            | REST error handling
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./springboot/SpringRestValidationHttpServer/index.html}Validation}} | Validate request payloads and path parameters using Bean Validation. | @Valid\
|                                                              |                                                            | ConstraintViolationException
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./springboot/SpringRestOpenApiHttpServer/index.html}OpenAPI / Swagger}} | Generate OpenAPI documentation from REST YAML endpoint declarations. | OpenAPI\
|                                                              |                                                            | Swagger UI
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./springboot/SpringRestCorsHttpServer/index.html}CORS}}   | Configure Cross-Origin Resource Sharing for REST endpoints. | CORS\
|                                                              |                                                            | @CrossOrigin
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./springboot/SpringRestSecurityHttpServer/index.html}Spring Security}} | Secure REST endpoints using Spring Security with OfficeFloor REST composition. | Spring Security\
|                                                              |                                                            | HTTP authorization
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./springboot/SpringRestDataJpaHttpServer/index.html}Spring Data JPA}} | Integrate Spring Data JPA repositories with transaction governance in REST YAML composition. | Spring Data JPA\
|                                                              |                                                            | @Transactional governance
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./springboot/SpringRestServletHttpServer/index.html}Servlet Interop}} | Inject HttpServletRequest and HttpServletResponse directly into REST service methods. | HttpServletRequest\
|                                                              |                                                            | HttpServletResponse
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./springboot/SpringRestQualifierHttpServer/index.html}Qualifier}} | Disambiguate multiple Spring beans of the same type using @Qualifier in service methods. | @Qualifier\
|                                                              |                                                            | Bean disambiguation
