*-------+------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| 2     | {{{./spring_migration/SpringWebFluxHttpServer/procedure.html}Spring Web Flux Procedures}} | Integrate @Controller methods as OfficeFloor Procedures to start using IOCC features. | Spring Web Flux Procedure
*-------+------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| 3     | {{{./spring_migration/SpringWebFluxHttpServer/migrate.html}Migrate Spring Web Flux}} | Remove the Spring Web Flux dependency and run natively on OfficeFloor. | Migrate Spring Web Flux
*-------+------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+


