** Infrastructure and Concurrency

  OfficeFloor's {{{https://sagenschneider.blogspot.com/2019/02/inversion-of-coupling-control.html}IOCC}} model provides fine-grained control over threads, start-up ordering, caching, and modularisation.  These tutorials explore that infrastructure layer.

*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
|| Tutorial                                                    || Description                                               || Covered
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/infrastructure/TeamHttpServer/index.html}Thread Injection}} | Assign specific thread teams to procedures to performance-tune the application. | Thread Injection
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/infrastructure/ThreadAffinityHttpServer/index.html}Thread Affinity}} | Bind procedures to CPU cores using the Executive for cache-friendly execution. | Executive
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/infrastructure/StartBeforeHttpServer/index.html}Start-up Ordering}} | Declare ordered start-up dependencies between ManagedObjectSource instances. | start-before , start-after
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/infrastructure/ConstantCacheHttpServer/index.html}Cache}} | Cache constant values to avoid repeated computation or lookup. | {{{/apidocs/net/officefloor/cache/Cache.html}Cache}}
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/infrastructure/ActivityHttpServer/index.html}Activity}} | Modularise REST YAML configuration into reusable Activity units. | Activity (Section)
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/infrastructure/TestHttpServer/index.html}Testing}} | Unit, system, and integration test OfficeFloor REST applications. | Unit / System / Integration testing
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+


** UI and Templates

  These tutorials demonstrate OfficeFloor's server-side template rendering capabilities.  Note: these tutorials use the XML-model WoOF template system and are candidates for refactoring to REST YAML composition.

*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
|| Tutorial                                                    || Description                                               || Covered
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/ui/StaticContentHttpServer/index.html}Static Content}} | Serve single page application files and other static assets. | /PUBLIC
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/ui/PrototypeHttpServer/index.html}Wireframe Prototyping}} | Build working wireframe prototypes and extend them into full applications. | #\{link\}
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/ui/DynamicHttpServer/index.html}Dynamic Web Page}} | Render dynamic content into WoOF templates. | $\{bean ... $\} , $\{property\}
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/ui/InteractiveHttpServer/index.html}Interactive Web Page}} | Handle form submissions and link clicks in interactive pages. | #\{link\} , @HttpParameters
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/ui/RawHttpServer/index.html}Generating HTML}}    | Render raw generated HTML into a WoOF template. | @UnescapedHtml
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/ui/JavaScriptApp/index.html}AJAX}}               | Service AJAX requests from JavaScript within a WoOF template page. | @HttpObject , ObjectResponse\
|                                                              |                                                            | @NotRenderTemplateAfter
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/ui/SectionHttpServer/index.html}Sectioning Content}} | Render sections of a WoOF template independently. | \<!-- \{section\} --\>
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/ui/InheritHttpServer/index.html}Template Inheritance}} | Inherit and override sections across WoOF templates. | \<!-- \{:override\} --\>\
|                                                              |                                                            | \<!-- \{!\} --\>
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| {{{./native/ui/NavigateHttpServer/index.html}Continuation Injection}} | Control execution flow across procedures without tight coupling. | @Next , @FlowInterface\
|                                                              |                                                            | Continuation Injection
*--------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+


